CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg. 1 reads:"President Kennedy Stumps Area for Democrats- Pitt's Field House was hammed with more than 8,000 of the party faithful at the Friday night rally where the Democratic party chief, President Kennedy, roasted the Republicans."
TitMainTitle: President Kennedy in Pittsburgh: President Kennedy addressing crowd from stage, with Kennedy banner above, in University of Pittsburgh field house
